<template>
  <section class="app-main">
    <transition name="fade-transform" mode="out-in">
      <keep-alive>
        <router-view :key="key" />
      </keep-alive>
    </transition>
  </section>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: 'AppMain',
  computed: {
    key() {
      return this.$route.path
    }
  }
}
</script>

<style lang="scss" scoped>
  .app-main {
    /* 50= navbar  50  */
    min-height: calc(100vh - 50px);
    width: 100%;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  .fixed-header+.app-main {
    padding-top: 50px;
  }
  
  .hasTagsView {
    .app-main {
      /* 84 = navbar + tags-view = 50 + 34 */
      min-height: calc(100vh - 84px);
    }
  
    .fixed-header+.app-main {
      padding-top: 84px;
    }
  }
  </style>
  
  <style lang="scss">
   /* fix css style bug in open el-dialog */
  .el-popup-parent--hidden {
    .fixed-header {
      padding-right: 15px;
    }
  }
  </style>
